    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是否曾想象穿过镜子，去邂逅你的“倒影”？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为拯救被困在镜中的双胞胎姐姐丽亚，少女亚丽踏上了跨越镜像的冒险之旅。她唯一的能力，便是穿越镜面、行走于镜像空间 —— 而这里的每一处倒影都真实可触：镜子里的路径能踏足，镜子里的机关能触发，镜子里的世界能交互。你将通过移动、旋转镜子操控周遭一切，用想象力搭建新路径，在虚实交织中破解谜题，奔赴终点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677100/extras/16f8030b2c0684a0b79e2700edadf718.poster.avif?t=1771191891\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677100/extras/16f8030b2c0684a0b79e2700edadf718.webm?t=1771191891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677100/extras/16f8030b2c0684a0b79e2700edadf718.mp4?t=1771191891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677100/extras/bc6c0209c39f09a73996234dc5d63693.avif?t=1771191891\" width=600 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来自纽约大学游戏专业团队开发的《亚丽亚的倒影》是一款曾荣获海内外多个奖项及提名、并于 2023 年提名 “最佳创新设计大奖” 的国风 3D 视觉解谜游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏获得了国内外多个机构的的认可，受到纽约大学的独立游戏设计风格影响，融合了对解谜游戏的热爱，也基于创作者本身对生命的经历和思考。游戏获得了多个国内外奖项，包括：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2020英特尔高校游戏展提名作品</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2020 AT&amp;T Unlocked游戏大赛提名作品</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2020年纽约大学游戏中心孵化器作品</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2022 Draknek New Voice 解谜游戏基金获得者</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2023第十五届厦门国际动漫节“金海豚奖”游戏作品大赛最佳游戏策划提名</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2023 中国游戏创新大赛最佳创新设计奖</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2023 中国游戏创新大赛最佳创新游戏大奖提名</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677100/extras/c3ccafa6e3df51b4cd74b4d486bc1f80.poster.avif?t=1771191891\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677100/extras/c3ccafa6e3df51b4cd74b4d486bc1f80.webm?t=1771191891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677100/extras/c3ccafa6e3df51b4cd74b4d486bc1f80.mp4?t=1771191891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677100/extras/0b0409c763cc3ba2da616cb3a0fcb5a6.avif?t=1771191891\" width=600 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《亚丽亚的倒影》集结了曾为《艾尔登法环》《街头霸王 5》《最终幻想 15：刺客庆典》献艺的顶尖乐手，以 “镜像” 为核心创作理念，将二胡、笛、箫等中国传统乐器与西洋小提琴融合，打造 “东西交融的镜像音域”。主旋律通过音符反转、旋律倒放、音频逆向等形式贯穿全曲，隐喻镜子映照万物的万千形态，将你深度代入亚丽与丽亚的羁绊故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677100/extras/2d1f0b2c5c1b57c7dd45df7d59e59380.poster.avif?t=1771191891\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677100/extras/2d1f0b2c5c1b57c7dd45df7d59e59380.webm?t=1771191891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677100/extras/2d1f0b2c5c1b57c7dd45df7d59e59380.mp4?t=1771191891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br>                       </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677100/extras/b0894feb682bd30c5d52cf15146f4411.avif?t=1771191891\" width=600 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创新镜像机制：打破虚实边界，镜像不再是单纯投影，而是可探索、可交互的真实空间，每一次穿镜都是全新解谜视角。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸式国风探索：遍历 7 个风格迥异的国风场景，从水墨竹林到琉璃镜宫，在东方美学画卷中解锁支线、密室与隐藏彩蛋。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >硬核解谜挑战：攻克 100 + 精心设计的谜题，解锁隐藏区域中看似不可能的挑战，收集镜碎片，唤醒亚丽与丽亚尘封的姐妹记忆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677100/extras/8cd4693e979a7913155fd192ea46bffa.poster.avif?t=1771191891\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677100/extras/8cd4693e979a7913155fd192ea46bffa.webm?t=1771191891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677100/extras/8cd4693e979a7913155fd192ea46bffa.mp4?t=1771191891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677100/extras/565ff35fd8b41264f0420235e63f9fc1.avif?t=1771191891\" width=600 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以镜子为核心进行多种类型的空间解谜。其中创新性使用了镜子以及多种镜子相关玩法，甚至探索了水面倒影、镜像递归，乃至镜子解谜boss战，创造了非常丰富的视觉以及玩法体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677100/extras/ee7f5d648c0dc63623c7b07b372df634.poster.avif?t=1771191891\" width=1138 height=638 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677100/extras/ee7f5d648c0dc63623c7b07b372df634.webm?t=1771191891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677100/extras/ee7f5d648c0dc63623c7b07b372df634.mp4?t=1771191891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677100/extras/936b554b5653ab622d7029396d0af582.avif?t=1771191891\" width=600 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >明线是玩家在镜像世界的冒险，暗线是每次打破魔镜之后主角对现实世界的回忆，隐藏线是双胞胎姐姐的视角，会在玩家完成高难度关卡收集齐镜碎片后解锁。在游戏场景中散落灵魂的碎片化叙事，一方面起到提示的作用，另一方面以诗意和哲思丰富世界观。主题曲以及整体叙事原自主创的真实生活经历，探讨如何在重要的人离世之后与世界和自我和解。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677100/extras/52e03ed6cdd6842212d097fc73107b56.poster.avif?t=1771191891\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677100/extras/52e03ed6cdd6842212d097fc73107b56.webm?t=1771191891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677100/extras/52e03ed6cdd6842212d097fc73107b56.mp4?t=1771191891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《亚丽亚的倒影》正是这样一款中国风的3D视觉解谜游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了拯救“被困在镜中的双胞胎姐姐”，少女亚丽踏上了旅途。她唯一的能力是穿越镜子，行走于镜像空间。而这些镜像都是“真实”的——镜子里的路径也可以行走，镜子里的机关也可以触发，等等。你需要利用镜像与想象力，破解谜题，抵达终点。探索由现实与镜像交织而成的世界，去寻找那个藏于镜中的答案吧。</p>",
